name: Capital Group Global Equity Select ETFTM (Canada)
longDescription: The Fund may invest its assets on a global basis, primarily in common stocks, including growth-oriented stocks, in depositary receipts and may invest in issuers in developed countries or developing countries.  Fund seeks Longterm growth of capital.
